# Day 07 - SPEED TYPING

## Jenkins pipeline - Parameterized

pipeline {
    agent any
    parameters {
        string(name: 'ENVIRONMENT',defaultValue: 'dev', 'Deployment Environment')
    }
    environment {
        INSTITUTE_NAME = "Pathnex"
    }
    stages {
        stage('Checkout') 
            steps {
                git url: 'https://github.com/sumit-pathnex/sample-java-app.git'
        }
        stage('Deploy') {
            steps {
                sh 'echo "Deploying to $ENVIRONMENT by $INSTITUTE_NAME"'

            }
        }

    }
}

## GitLab CI - Parameterized via Variables

stages:
    - deploy

variable:
  INSTITUTE_NAME: "sumit-pathnex"
  ENVIRONMENT: "dev"


deploy:
  stage: deploy
  script:
    - echo "Deploying to $ENVIRONMENT by $INSTITUTE_NAME"
    
